    {
        "url": "/quotes/romesh_gunesekera_734344",
        "quote": "The nationalist movement supported Sinhala by suppressing Tamil; there were competing nationalisms. It was a fundamental mistake to make parallel streams in education - or a calculated political gamble. Politicians were playing with it.",
