    {
        "url": "/quotes/romesh_gunesekera_734347",
        "quote": "In the sense that writing is to retrieve the past and stop the passing of time, all writing is about loss. It's not nostalgia in the sense of yearning to bring back the past, but recognition of the erosion of things as you live.",
