    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/romesh_gunesekera_734354",
        "quote": "I was thinking of writers living in East Europe before the Berlin Wall came down. They wrote fantastic stuff but were dealing with a situation that was almost impossible to deal with, but they found a way.",
